channel.title: Need JDK 6.0 or 5.0
channel.description:
Hello, I am creating my own server, and Ive been looking everywhere for JDK 5.0 or 6.0....Ive been unsecsseful...I read somewhere earlier that I need to be sent the file to be able to use it...
So unless Im sent the file, Im not able to compile...Hey that rhymed!
Anyways, is it true I need to be sent the file?
And if so, am I allowed to post anywhere asking for the file to be sent to me?..
Thanks!
EDIT: Nevermind....I didnt find it...thread still open

item.description:
@Play_N_Skillz wrote:

You probably remember me from MT’s guide to private server. I had the same trouble as you. So, I downloaded JDK 5 update 9 and did some fixing with the codes in Compile and Runserver and switched them to format my java type. Then I compiled and Ran it and it worked.

Maybe this might be some help to you.
